		description: ["Pam's Harvestcraft 2 Food Core adds a complete cooking toolkit on top of the crop layer. Unlike Farmer's Delight's placed blocks, each Pam's tool is a handheld crafting ingredient — place it in the crafting grid alongside food items to process them. None of them are consumed by recipes; they stay in your inventory indefinitely.", "The Grinder mills grain into flour. The Juicer extracts fruit juice. The Mixing Bowl makes dough and batter. The Pot simmers dairy, meat, and soups. The Roller flattens dough into pasta and presses nuts into oil. The Saucepan reduces milk into yogurt or caramel. The Bakeware handles pies, cakes, and muffins. All seven tools are cheap to craft and non-consumable."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "0000000000013011"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "pamhc2foodcore:grinderitem", Count: 1b}
