		}]
	}, {
		id: "0000000000013050"
		x: 8.0d
		y: 32.0d
		dependencies: ["0000000000013020", "0000000000013030"]
		title: "From the Dairy"
		icon: {id: "pamhc2foodcore:cheeseitem", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Butter is made by simmering milk in the Pot — just the Pot and a milk bucket. Cheese adds salt to the same process: Pot, milk, salt. Both are essential to the cooking chain: butter goes into mashed potatoes and pastries, cheese into mac and cheese, grilled cheese, and crackers.", "Establish a reliable milk source before going deeper into Pam's cooking. Passive cows near your base are fine early on. The investment pays dividends across dozens of recipes and both dairy products appear consistently through the sweet and savory sides of the kitchen."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "0000000000013051"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "pamhc2foodcore:butteritem", Count: 1b}
			count: 2L
		}, {
			id: "0000000000013052"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "pamhc2foodcore:cheeseitem", Count: 1b}
			count: 2L
		}]
		rewards: [{
			id: "0000000000013053"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "minecraft:sugar", Count: 16b}
		}]
	}, {
		id: "0000000000013060"
		x: 10.0d
		y: 32.0d
		dependencies: ["0000000000013050"]
		title: "The Baker's Prep"
		icon: {id: "pamhc2foodcore:doughitem", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Dough and Batter are the two base forms for all baked goods in Pam's. Dough is flour, water, and salt in the Mixing Bowl — two per craft. It goes into pies and soft pretzels, and rolls into pasta with the Roller. Batter is flour, milk, and an egg in the Mixing Bowl — also two per craft. It goes into cakes, muffins, and donuts.", "Both can be prepared in advance and held in a chest. Batch a stack of each before starting a baking session. Once your flour and dairy supply is running, prepping these two takes under a minute and unlocks the entire baking tree."]
		tasks: [{
			id: "0000000000013061"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "pamhc2foodcore:doughitem", Count: 1b}
			count: 2L
		}, {
			id: "0000000000013062"
			type: "item"
			item: {id: "pamhc2foodcore:batteritem", Count: 1b}
			count: 2L
		}]
		rewards: [{
